title: Shark® Rotator® Professional Lift-Away® NV500: Commercial
description:
Shark® has redefined the vacuum industry again! The revolutionary, high-performance Rotator® Lift-Away® is like three incredible vacuums in one!

A powerful upright, a lift-away® for portable cleaning, and with an optional caddy, the lift-away® is ultra convenient! Learn more about the Shark® Rotator® Professional Lift-Away® by visiting http://www.sharkclean.com/rotator/
